---
title: HelloHero: Halloumi & Creamy Onion Sauce with Mashed Potato
description: Serve up a comforting meal that's as good as a hug! With tender, flavoursome halloumi in a creamy sauce and loads of satisfying
mash, this dinner will make you feel all snuggly - perfect for a home-cooked meal with heart.

